sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:modificationsToBackbone: replaced pPGK promoter in pRRL.cPPT.PGK-GFP.WPRE.Sin-18 with approx. 1350 bp human 5' FOXA2 promoter region using 5' XhoI and 3' AgeI restriction sites.
